Multiple federal agencies have contributed to the contents of this layer and it is in a continuous state of update. Source and date of feature updates are tracked to the feature level.</abstract>    <purpose>This layer provides an answer for the question of who is the administrator of a federally held parcel of land. It was created as a national reference theme for use with the GeoCommunicator's Land Manager Viewer.</purpose>    <supplinf>This layer is a dynamic assembly of spatial data layers maintained at various federal and local government offices. The best known available data layers from these souces have been harvested and integrated into this layer. This layer represents a work in progress.</supplinf>   </descript>   <timeperd>    <timeinfo>     <rngdates>      <begdate>19970101</begdate>      <enddate>20090101</enddate>     </rngdates>    </timeinfo>    <current>publication date</current>   </timeperd>   <status>    <progress>In work</progress>    <update>Quartely</update>   </status>   <spdom>    <bounding>     <westbc>-113.6029416</westbc>     <eastbc>-106.927117</eastbc>     <northbc>41.00236956</northbc>     <southbc>36.18672755</southbc>    </bounding>   </spdom>   <keywords>    <theme><themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Category</themekt><themekey>boundaries</themekey></theme><theme><themekt>BLM-Theme</themekt><themekey>Authorization</themekey><themekey>Management</themekey></theme><theme><themekt>BLM-REA</themekt><themekey>COP</themekey><themekey>Colorado Plateau</themekey></theme><theme><themekt>BLM-State</themekt><themekey>Arizona</themekey><themekey>Colorado</themekey><themekey>New Mexico</themekey><themekey>Utah</themekey></theme><theme><themekt>None</themekt><themekey>DOI</themekey><themekey>Bureau of Land Management</themekey><themekey>BLM</themekey><themekey>Rapid Ecoregional Assessment</themekey><themekey>REA</themekey></theme><theme>     <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Category Name</themekt>     <themekey>planningCadastre</themekey>    </theme>    <theme>     <themekt>None</themekt>     <themekey>Federal Land Stewardship</themekey>     <themekey>LST</themekey>     <themekey>SMA</themekey>     <themekey>Land Status</themekey>     <themekey>Surface Management Agency</themekey>     <themekey>Federal Land</themekey>     <themekey>Public Land</themekey>     <themekey>Ownership</themekey>    </theme>    <theme>     <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Category Code</themekt>     <themekey>015</themekey>    </theme>    <theme>     <themekt>H-9161-1 BLM Manual 9160 -
